---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="About - Simon Gelbart" current="about">
  <section class="page-heading narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>French senior backend developer interested in tooling, architecture, and deterministic systems.</h1>
    <p class="lede">I use this site as a public home for personal projects: libraries, CLIs, automation tools, learning material, and backend architecture experiments.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="section split">
    <div><p class="eyebrow">Technical focus</p><h2>What I keep coming back to</h2></div>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>Backend architecture and software design</li>
      <li>Developer productivity and workflow tooling</li>
      <li>Performance-aware library design</li>
      <li>Reproducibility, evaluation, and orchestration</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
